item.title: 9/11, did bush planned it?
item.dc:creator: @PaulT PaulT
item.description:
@PaulT wrote:

I dont know. There just isnt a chance... I dont get it..

Think about it this way: Pearl Harbour was completely preventable. There were many warnings. Our government ignored them.

World War 2 allowed the personal income tax laws to pass, and remain after World War 2, which is unconstitutional, and completely against the principles upon which our country was founded.

9/11 was preventable, at least. This is a breakdown of the governments official report on 9/11 and it’s inaccuracies:
http://video.google.com/videoplay?docid=6837001821567284154&q=9%2F11+report

What did the government/business interests in high offices have to gain from 9/11?
Is it possible the government started false conspiracy rumours (loose change, etc…) to throw us off the real track?
